根据[[联合国教育、科学及文化组织|联合国教科文组织]]1972年制订的《[[保护世界文化和自然遗产公约|保护世界文化和自然遗产公约]]》，[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]是指对全人类有重要[[文化遗产|文化]]或[[自然遗产|自然]]价值的遗产项目<ref name="convention">{{cite web | url = https://whc.unesco.org/en/convention/ | title = The World Heritage Convention | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200708155811/http://whc.unesco.org/en/convention/ | publisher = UNESCO World Heritage Centre | accessdate = 2020-07-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-07-08}}</ref>。[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]于1992年3月31日接受公约，该国自然和文化遗迹因此有资格列入《[[世界遗产名录|世界遗产名录]]》<ref name="unesco1">{{cite web  | url = https://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/lt | title = Lithuania | publisher = UNESCO World Heritage Centre | accessdate = 2020-07-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200623043420/https://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/lt/ | archivedate = 2020-06-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。截至2020年，该国共有四处遗产入选，均为文化遗产。首先是1994年列入的[[维尔纽斯旧城|维尔纽斯历史中心]]，此后又在2000、2004和2005年各有一项遗产入选<ref>{{Cite web | date = 2019-06-19 | accessdate = 2020-07-27 | deadurl = yes | url = https://lietuva.lt/en/naujienos/unesco-world-heritage-sites-to-visit-in-lithuania/ | title = Lithuania | UNESCO World Heritage sites to visit in Lithuania | author = Jurgita Laurinėnaitė-Šimelevičienė | website = lietuva.lt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720123035/https://lietuva.lt/en/naujienos/unesco-world-heritage-sites-to-visit-in-lithuania/ | archivedate = 2020-07-20 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | date = 2017-04-25 | accessdate = 2020-07-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720091949/https://www.worldatlas.com/articles/unesco-world-heritage-sites-in-lithuania.html | url = https://www.worldatlas.com/articles/unesco-world-heritage-sites-in-lithuania.html | title = UNESCO World Heritage Sites In Lithuania | website = WorldAtlas | author = Gregory Sousa | archivedate = 2020-07-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.truelithuania.com/unesco-sites-in-lithuania-4438 | title = UNESCO sites in Lithuania « True Lithuania | website = www.truelithuania.com | author = Augustinas Žemaitis | accessdate = 2020-07-27}}</ref>。四项遗产中有半数是跨国遗产项目，分别是与[[俄罗斯世界遗产列表|俄罗斯]]分享的[[库尔斯沙嘴|库尔斯沙嘴]]，与其他九个国家共同拥有的[[斯特鲁维测地弧|斯特鲁维地理探测弧线]]<ref name="unesco1" />。

除已入选的四项世界遗产外，立陶宛还有两项遗产列入预备名单<ref name="unesco1" />。任何遗产提名《世界遗产名录》前都必须入选预备名单。

